  "private": true,
  "description": "HTTP + SSE shared TypeScript types for the widget <-> service contract: /v1/help/message, /v1/help/stream, /v1/help/escalate, /v1/tickets, ContextSnapshot, and the SSE event union.",
  "license": "UNLICENSED",
  "type": "module",
